<HEAD>Three Environmentalists Arrested</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Three members of a radical Arizona
environmental group were arrested on charges they conspired to
sabotage two nuclear power plants and an Energy Department bomb
