   A third man was arrested in Tucson on charges of conspiring with
the others to sabotage commercial nuclear power plants at Palo
Verde, Ariz., and near San Luis Obispo, Calif., as well as the
federal government's Rocky Flats Nuclear Weapons Plant near Golden,
Colo.
