<FIRST>u i AM-Dollar-Yen     06-01 0028</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Dollar-Yen,0028</SECOND>
<HEAD>Dollar Down</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The dollar opened at 142.12 yen on the Tokyo
foreign exchange market Friday, down from Thursday's close of
142.52 yen.
