Reynolds of Sacramento said Price should be a candidate for league
MVP honors.
   But he quickly added Mark won't get it.
   ``Little guys almost never get it,'' Reynolds commented. ``But I
think he's as deserving as anybody. He's so quick you need to hit
him on the head with something to stop him. He also is an excellent
of offensive player.''
