   (The solar-powered light is manufactured by Intermatic Inc.,
Intermatic Plaza, Spring Grove, IL 60081; the hand sander by DYI,
3M Center, St. Paul, MN 55144; the utility knife by Stanley Tools,
600 Myrtle St., New Britain, CT 06050; the tweezer by Overview
