to 77~ in active trading. Freddie Mac, as it is known, declared a
40-cents-a-share quarterly dividend on the preferred shares, and a
sharply increased payout on its common stock, which is owned by the
Federal Home Loan Bank Board.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks
gained .91 to 179.76. At the American Stock Exchange, the market
value index was up 1.29 at 357.95.
   Volume on the Big Board came to 149.95 million shares with an
hour to go.
